title: Something's Gotta Give!
description:
Linda and Emily go around the league pointing out who we're disappointed with: included but not limited to the Pittsburgh Penguins and the Vancouver Canucks. After that they get into their game of the week before highlighting the NY Islanders' first home game in their new arena. Lastly, Linda leaves us with a few comments that might upset a few Seattle fans!
